'''"Tears of Aquanna"''' was a [[Music/Legends|song]] performed by [[Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes/Legends|Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes]]. It was considered a favorite by band member [[Ickabel G'ont/Legends|Ickabel G'ont]] because it allowed him the opportunity for a long, elaborate [[Fanfar/Legends|Fanfar]] solo.

